overview: Once you check in the Jock Inn and get a good look around, trust us...you won't want to leave. From the smoking hot waiters and chefs to the totally ripped athletes that are staying at the hotel, dreamy studs just can't be avoided. And for that reason, sexual tension constantly runs high! Watch as these guys hook up for hardcore ass-poundings in the kitchen, wild and spontaneous threesomes and even special ways of pleasing angry guests! From start to finish, you won't want to miss what goes on behind these closed doors!
title: Jock Inn
